      <title>乌克兰寻找电网设备和弹药以避免夏季停电</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ukraine-hunts-for-power-equipment-ammunition-to-avoid-summer-blackouts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[乌克兰能源部长格尔曼·加卢申科表示，乌克兰需要改进防空系统，以保护其能源资产免受俄罗斯导弹袭击，并避免今年夏天用电接近冬季高峰时出现停电。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/ukraine-hunts-for-power-equipment-ammunition-to-avoid-summer-blackouts</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
