      <title>开发商押注 Bankside 是伦敦后疫情时代的办公热点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/developer-bets-bankside-is-london-s-post-covid-office-hotspot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[Land Securities Group Plc 收购了 Bankside 的一块开发地块，认为该地区位于泰晤士河南岸，能够充分利用新冠疫情后伦敦办公生活的转变。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/developer-bets-bankside-is-london-s-post-covid-office-hotspot</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 07:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
