    <item>
      <title>印度寻求每年1000亿美元的外国直接投资以吸引中国套期保值者</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/india-seeks-100-billion-a-year-in-fdi-as-it-woos-china-hedgers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一位高级官员表示，印度的目标是每年吸引至少 1000 亿美元的外国直接投资总额，因为这个南亚国家正在吸引寻求多元化投资、远离中国的投资者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-06/india-seeks-100-billion-a-year-in-fdi-as-it-woos-china-hedgers</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 06 Apr 2024 02:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
